	* libtool.m4 (LT_CMD_MAX_LEN): Try using getconf to set
	lt_cv_sys_max_cmd_len.

2007-05-28  Peter O'Gorman  <peter@pogma.com>

	* ltmain.in, libtool.m4 [darwin]: Only use ${wl} in verstring
	with xlc.

