	* libltdl/ltdl.c (lt_dlexit): Make sure that 'cur' is not NULL
	before checking that it is still in the list.

2007-01-28  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

	* ltmain.in (link mode): Pass through `-p' and `-fprofile-*' for
	GCC.

