	* libtool.m4 (AC_LIBTOOL_SYS_GLOBAL_SYMBOL_PIPE): Unicos 9 sed rejects
	empty parentheses as in 's/x\(\)/\1/'.
	(AC_LIBTOOL_PROG_COMPILER_PIC) [unicos*]: wl=-Wl,.

	* tests/quote.test: Match link quoting against `"$wl"', not `-Wl,'.

