	* libtoolize.in: Install `install-sh' as well, needed for configure ..
	* Makefile.am: .. install, update it.
	* NEWS, doc/libtool.texi (Distributing): .. document it.
	Reported by Ross Boylan <ross@biostat.ucsf.edu>.

